updateDimensionFieldValues

private void updateDimensionFieldValues()
Update the 'Cells per line', 'Lines per page' and 'Margin' field values. This method is called when the respective settings have possibly changed because the user changed one of these values.

updateDimensionFields

private void updateDimensionFields()
                            throws com.sun.star.uno.Exception
Update the maximum, minimum and current values and the states (enabled or dissabled) of the 'Cells per line', 'Lines per page' and 'Margin' field values on the 'Export/Emboss' tab. This method is called when the respective braille settings have possibly changed because another paper size was selected.
